		<RichText x="62" y="534" width="289" height="113" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="32" color="#ffffff">无相之岩·奏鸣曲<br/><span fontSize="60">磐石之心</span></p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#ffe599" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="575" y="52" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="48" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffffff" width="318" height="51" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="48" color="#ffffff">全技能一图流</p>
			</content>
			<filters>
				<DropShadowFilter angle="40" color="#ffe599" distance="16" alpha="0.75" quality="2" blurX="25" blurY="25"/>
			</filters>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1200" width="423" height="135" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">玄武岩柱：<span color="#ffe599">24岩</span><span>盾，击破可产生1-2个</span><span color="#ffe599">岩元素晶球</span><span>；受到<br/>突刺/穿刺-</span><span color="#ffe599">0.2岩</span><span>，切割-</span><span color="#ffe599">0.28岩</span><span>。<br/>复苏玄武岩柱：</span><span color="#ffe599">8岩</span><span>盾，击破可产生1-2个</span><span color="#ffe599">岩元素晶球</span><span>；受到<br/>突刺/穿刺-</span><span color="#ffe599">0.24岩</span><span>，切割-</span><span color="#ffe599">0.32岩</span><span>。<br/>黄岩块：</span><span color="#ffe599">3岩</span><span>盾，击破可产生持续14.4s的护罩；受到<br/>突刺/穿刺-</span><span color="#ffe599">0.2岩</span><span>，切割-</span><span color="#ffe599">0.28岩</span><span>。<br/>岩棱：</span><span color="#ffe599">2岩</span><span>盾，全部击破以打断鎏金岩潮。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="77" y="692" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" fontWeight="normal" color="#ffe599" width="206" height="43" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W04" fontSize="40" fontStyle="italic" color="#ffe599">「贝撒纳」</p>
