		</Group>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之岩脱去外壳，短暂暴露核心，在自身和周围3个位置升起玄武岩柱，生成玄武岩柱的区域造成<span color="#ffe599">25%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(无数字)</span><span>。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="439" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之岩暴露核心，施放岩封印标记同步于玩家，随后岩封印触发3次崩破，前两次造成<span color="#ffe599">50%</span><span>伤害，第三次造成</span><span color="#ffe599">75%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="927" width="428" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之岩化作成大锤，蓄力后重重砸下，造成<span color="#ffe599">150%</span><span>伤害，锤击处扩散出3个碎岩波，每个造成</span><span color="#ffe599">50%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="927" width="438" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之岩升空，激发其下方的玄武岩柱，使其产生一个冲击波，造成<span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，但据说可以跳起来躲冲击波。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1151" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之岩升空，脱去外壳，激发其下方的玄武岩柱，使其破裂爆炸造成<span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害，留下一片流沙持续造成</span><span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="1375" width="423" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之岩的玄武岩柱被强化后，其周期性朝玩家发射砂砾弹，每个造成<span color="#ffe599">25%,17.5%,12.5%,5%,2.5%</span><span>伤害，可被护罩抵挡。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="424" height="143" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之岩盘旋升空，激发所有玄武岩柱，玄武岩柱产生共鸣波，每次造成<span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害</span><span color="#ffbfbf">(闪避帧无效)</span><span>，持续8-9次，其下方会产生一个黄岩块，击破以获得躲避冲击波的护罩。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
