		<RichText x="738" y="447" fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff" width="439" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之岩升空开阵，8个岩立方围一圈暴露核心，将岩立方粉碎成为岩元素晶华，强化在场的玄武岩柱进行攻击。</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="424" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">无相之岩将外壳化为成两面墙，随后夹击，造成<span color="#ffe599">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1375" width="442" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">生命值低于5%时，无相之岩召唤3个玄武岩柱，复苏持续15s，每个玄武岩柱恢复无相之岩<span color="#ffe599">15%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#937122" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#937122">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
